descript.abstract: Polygons of aerial survey area in wetland habitats of the Copper River Delta, Alaska for dusky Canada goose population surveys This survey area was sampled by systematic strip transects 400 meters wide in spring 1986-2008.
descript.purpose: Objectives of the survey were to estimate population size, trend, and distribution of dusky Canada geeses.
